Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:55.55,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,700)}Episode 49\N"Invasion of Black Riders"{NOTE:第49話\\N襲来！ブラックライダーズ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.08,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Who do you think these Black Riders are?{NOTE:何なの？ブラックライダーズって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:01.42,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,They call themselves Riders.{NOTE:ライダーズっと言うくらいだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:03.82,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,But are they really?{NOTE:ライダー何だろうけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:05.28,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Yeah…{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.98,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{\an8}And why did they kidnap Avinia?{NOTE:なぜアユリアを連れ去ったんだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:11.78,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seems like they're interested in her Kinship Stone. But why?{NOTE:絆石どうとか言ってたらしいなも。気になるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:13.78,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sure they have a reason.{NOTE:何か理由がありそうですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:14.95,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah.{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:18.02,Default2,Lute,0,0,0,,{\an8}Still, we have to save her somehow.{NOTE:何しても、アユリアを助けに行かないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:22.52,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Avinia is the one who went with you to the Tower of Illusion, huh?{NOTE:蜃気楼の塔へ一緒に行ったあのアユリアか。\\N(Tower of Illusion)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:24.58,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Hey, what kind of Rider was it that took her?{NOTE:ね、どんなライダーだったか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:26.98,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Could give us some more details?{NOTE:もうちょっと詳しく教えてもらえるかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:30.25,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,This portrait gives no clues at all.{NOTE:この似顔絵チャ は正直さっぱりだからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.22,Default,Chamo,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:36.45,Default,Chamo,0,0,0,,He was wearing this scary full body armor-nyaa.{NOTE:全身防具に身を包んで怖かったでしょにゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:39.38,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,So you couldn't see their face at all?{NOTE:つまり、顔が見えなかったってことね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:40.72,Default,Chamo,0,0,0,,Nyaa-ope.{NOTE:でしょにゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:44.12,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,The world was just saved from the Black Blight.{NOTE:せっかく黒の凶気から世界が救われたというのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:46.45,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,And now we have to deal with this right after…{NOTE:こんなことが起こるとはな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.78,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,What is your opinion on this, Chief Omna?{NOTE:どう思います、オムナ村長？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.12,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:56.02,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,If I recall correctly, Avinia was the only one who survived back then, right?{NOTE:アユリアは確かかつてあった、桑村のたった一人の生き残りやったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:56.88,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:04:01.42,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,That might be related to the current events.{NOTE:そのことと今回のことは何か関係があるやもしれんの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:02.32,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:あれ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:04.82,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,I don't know the details, but…{NOTE:私も詳しくは知らんのじゃが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:11.48,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,I heard that in Avinia's village there was a\hfamily that possessed special Rider powers.{NOTE:アユリアの村にはライダーとして特別な力を持つ一族がいたと聞いてやる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.88,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,A family with special powers?{NOTE:特別な力を持つ一族？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:15.55,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Precisely.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:21.52,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Perhaps the Riders who took Avinia knew about that family?{NOTE:じゃ、アユリアを連れ去ったライダー達もその一族のことを知ってると思ったのかも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.22,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Probably.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.98,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,I don't know anything for sure, however.{NOTE:定かなのことは分からんがな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:28.82,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Whether they knew or not, I won't forgive them!{NOTE:だからって、連れ去るなんて許せない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:29.58,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.75,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Those Black Riders…{NOTE:そのブラックライダーズは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:37.42,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,…they might be seeking a new kind of power.{NOTE:ライダーとしての特別な力を求めるnのかもしれない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.75,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Thinking back…{NOTE:俺も周りのことを考えす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.18,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,…I really wanted to be strong, too.{NOTE:ただただ強くなりたかったから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.88,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,We have to save Avinia.{NOTE:アユリアを助けにいかないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:48.02,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,You got that right.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Chief. We're free to go to save her, right?{NOTE:村長。アユリアを助けに行っていいよな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.55,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:56.32,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,I understand the feeling of wanting to help your friend very well.{NOTE:友を放っておけん気持ちはよく分かる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:05:01.18,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,But we must act carefully here.{NOTE:じゃが、ここはわれらも慎重に行動せねばならん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:05.18,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,That's right, Lute. Even if you go help, you need to be careful.{NOTE:そうだよ、リュート。助けに行くにしても、気をつけないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.35,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,I know. I won't do anything stupid.{NOTE:分かってる。無茶をしないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:11.35,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Lute has Navirou, the best navigator in the world!{NOTE:ま、リュートはこの世界一のナビゲーター、ナビルーがついてるから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:12.81,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Everything will be A-okay!{NOTE:…大丈夫。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:20.58,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Just who are these Black Riders?{NOTE:何何んだ、ブラックライダーズって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:52.18,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,Why do you want Kinship Stones so much?{NOTE:そんなにXXXが欲しいのですが？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:55.18,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,I know the answer to your question.{NOTE:私はその答えを知っていますが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:58.18,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,But I have no intention of sharing it with you.{NOTE:君に話すつもりはありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:01.98,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to know it.{NOTE:君が知る必要もありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.18,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Master Anubis.{NOTE:アンヴィス様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:06.62,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Can I put this thing in the lower zone?{NOTE:このものはローに入れておけば宜しいでしょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:11.62,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,She'll be a good girl now.{NOTE:ま、大人しく良い子にしてることだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.72,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,I bet she will.{NOTE:そう言うこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.82,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,If she doesn't want to get eaten by Lars, that is.{NOTE:ラースの兄貴に食われたくなかったらな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.42,Default,Lars,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!{NOTE:食っちまうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:26.82,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Chief Omna, what's our next move?{NOTE:オムナ村長。これからどうしますか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.25,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:33.08,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I don't want anyone to take any unnecessary risks.{NOTE:本当は皆を危険な目にあわせたくはないのじゃが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:36.05,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,However, trying to stop Lute is a risk in itself…{NOTE:ミュートは(XX・とめてもきかん)じゃろうし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.68,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Can't argue with you there.{NOTE:でしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:40.12,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.{NOTE:仕方ない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:45.25,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Dan, can you take Genie and the others with you?{NOTE:ダン。ジーニー達とともについていってもらえるかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:49.02,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,And if they complain about it, do your best to persuade them.{NOTE:そして無茶をしそうになったらさとしてやってくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:49.88,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.05,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Of course.{NOTE:もちろんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.38,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Chief, I have a favor to ask.{NOTE:村長、お願いです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.85,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,What is it, Nariki?{NOTE:どうした、ナリキ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.85,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Please let me go, too.{NOTE:自分も行かせてくださいっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:03.92,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I know I just became a Rider, but I want to be of use to everyone.{NOTE:せっかくライダーに成りたんす。皆の役に立ちたいっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:06.38,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,But you're still an apprentice.{NOTE:お前はまだ新米だろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:09.12,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I won't be a burden. I'll do my best.{NOTE:足纏いに成らないように、頑張るっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.75,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,So please…!{NOTE:だから、お願いします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:15.65,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,I see trying to stop you is dangerous as well…{NOTE:お前も(XX・止めてもきかん)ようじゃな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:17.62,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,You resemble Lute in many ways.{NOTE:リュートによく似ている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.65,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Then…!?{NOTE:じゃ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.68,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,However, Nariki.{NOTE:じゃがな、ナリキ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:32.45,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Protecting the village is an important task for a Rider.{NOTE:村を守ると言うことも、ライダーの大事な勤め一つじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:38.45,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,You will remain here, protecting the\hvillage while your seniors are away.{NOTE:お前は村に残り、先輩達に変わって村を守るじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.72,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,This is your duty now.{NOTE:それが今の御前の勤めじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.35,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Do you understand?{NOTE:分かるかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:48.52,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.{NOTE:はいっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:50.72,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I will protect the village.{NOTE:自分村を守る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.68,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,What do you think, Gale?{NOTE:どう思う、ゲイル。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:58.18,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Think about what, Shadow?{NOTE:何がっすか、シャドウの姉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.82,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,About bringing that little girl in here, of course.{NOTE:ここにあのお嬢ちゃんを連れてきたこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:08.02,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,What's the purpose of it?{NOTE:何の意味があるかね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:13.75,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,We've been stealing Kinship Stones up till now… but we've never caught a Rider.{NOTE:今まで絆石を奪ってもライダーをとらえたことなんかなかったのにね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.62,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,So what?{NOTE:そっすよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:19.22,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Master Anubis must have plans for her.{NOTE:アンヴィス様に何かを考えがあるのだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:24.18,Default,Lars,0,0,0,,But this girl has an impressive Kinship Stone.{NOTE:XXしても、あのお嬢ちゃんXXXな絆石を持ってたな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:33.32,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,This girl must have other Rider friends, I doubt they'll stay silent for long.{NOTE:私はあの嬢ちゃんの仲間のライダー達がこのまま黙って放っておくとは思えないね}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.88,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Friends? What friends?{NOTE:いるっすか、仲間なんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:42.05,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Wasn't her whole village annihilated?{NOTE:あいつの村は全滅したって話じゃないっすか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:44.12,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,She's all alone.{NOTE:一人ぼっちてわけだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:49.52,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,I wasn't talking about her village.{NOTE:XXの村の話じゃないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:53.52,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,There are other Riders in this world. The ones who stopped the Black Blight, for example.{NOTE:例の黒の凶気を止めたライダー連中の話さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:54.52,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,I see.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.62,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,The group from Hakum, huh?{NOTE:ハクムぐらのやつっすか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:09:02.18,Default,Lars,0,0,0,,Well, I will crush and eat anybody who stands in my way.{NOTE:ま、俺らの邪魔するやつはXX食っちまえばいいのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:11.85,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Those Riders already know that we're searching for Kinship Stones.{NOTE:いずれにしても、私たちが絆石が狩りをしていることがすでにライダーたちに知れ渡っているでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:15.15,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,This will be interesting.{NOTE:面白くなってきたということです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:22.78,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,It'll be satisfying, seeing those incompetent Riders tremble in fear of us.{NOTE:無能なライダー達が私たちに恐れおののく姿を想像するのは気持ちの良いものです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:29.05,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,Mad, if you let your guard down with me, you'll regret it.{NOTE:マッド。油断してると痛い目にあうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:31.78,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,It will be interesting, though.{NOTE:それも面白そうだけどね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.88,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,I will take you on any time.{NOTE:いつでも受けて立ちますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:42.82,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,My goal is to capture the Kinship Stone of the Rider who flies a Rathalos.{NOTE:私の狙いは隻眼のリオレウスに乗るライダーの絆石を奪い取ることですから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:47.25,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You're referring to Lute?{NOTE:ミュートとか言うやつだよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.92,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,I'm interested in his Kinship Stone myself.{NOTE:夏の絆石俺も興味あるよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.98,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,Are you going to approach him, Gale?{NOTE:やるつもりだね、ゲイル？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.55,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,Because I won't let you.{NOTE:そうはさえないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:58.18,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Well, look at that. Shadow is interested as well.{NOTE:なんだ、シャドウの姉さんも興味あるっすか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.88,Default,Lars,0,0,0,,Wait, wait. I want it too.{NOTE:待て、待て。俺だって欲しいぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:03.48,Default,Lars,0,0,0,,His Kinship Stone is mine!{NOTE:あいつの絆石は俺のものんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:05.22,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,Oh really?{NOTE:どうだろうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.18,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Fools.{NOTE:おろかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:13.15,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,All Kinship Stones belong to Master Anubis.{NOTE:全ての絆石はアンヴィス様に捧げるものです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:16.22,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,We're only here to fulfill our duty.{NOTE:我々はその責務を果たすまで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.98,Default,Anubis,0,0,0,,I need that Kinship Stone.{NOTE:あの絆石が必要だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:25.45,Default,Anubis,0,0,0,,The one that belongs to the Rider flying a Rathalos.{NOTE:強く力を持つであろう隻眼のリオレウスのライダーの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.22,Default,Anubis,0,0,0,,Go, Gale.{NOTE:行け、ゲイル。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.18,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!{NOTE:よし！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:31.68,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Roger that, Master Anubis.{NOTE:了解です、アンヴィス様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:34.52,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mad and Lars.{NOTE:悪いね、マッドXラース兄貴。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.08,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Shadow.{NOTE:シャドウの姉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.38,Default,Lars,0,0,0,,Tsk! Why you?{NOTE:ち！何でお前が？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.02,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,I don't like this.{NOTE:気に入らないね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:45.25,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,Very well. Let's see what you've got.{NOTE:ま、お手並み拝見といきましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.15,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,All right, Nariki!{NOTE:よし、ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.58,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Try to "Ride On".{NOTE:Ride onをしてみろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.02,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!{NOTE:はいっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.82,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,You can do it, Nariki.{NOTE:頑張れ、ナリキ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.62,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,You're the village protector.{NOTE:村を守るんだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:59.62,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:Ride On!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.15,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Velocidrome!{NOTE:ドスランポス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.05,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,All right!{NOTE:よしゃ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:05.92,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Nice!{NOTE:いいぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:07.62,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I did it.{NOTE:やった！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:09.15,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I did it!{NOTE:やったんっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:12.88,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,Hey, Nariki!{NOTE:こら、ナリキ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.72,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,Don't just aimlessly run around!{NOTE:考え無しに、寝るんじゃない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:18.95,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,You must bond with it first!{NOTE:まずは男っと心をひとつにするのじゃ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.02,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Okay!{NOTE:はいっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:22.25,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,I get it!{NOTE:分かってるっすよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:23.35,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Yahoo!{NOTE:やほ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:25.28,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Onwards, onwards!{NOTE:行け、行け！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.45,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Good luck, Nariki.{NOTE:頑張れ、ナリキ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.35,Default,Genie,0,0,0,,Make sure you take this seriously.{NOTE:真面目に遣れ、真面目に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:38.02,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,He's been always like this.{NOTE:ずっとXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:42.42,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Well, it's the birth of a new Rider.{NOTE:ま、XX新たなライダーの誕生じゃな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.58,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,It is.{NOTE:ですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:46.92,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,And I have to work hard too.{NOTE:私も頑張らないとな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:50.82,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Oh? By the way…{NOTE:お？あ、その…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:53.88,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Why are there Riders that steal Kinship Stones?{NOTE:なんで絆石を奪うライダー達がいるのか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.82,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,What's their goal in doing that?{NOTE:その目的は何のか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:58.58,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,I wanted to investigate it as a squad member.{NOTE:書士隊員として調べてみたいと思って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.38,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:お。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:04.75,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,I am planning to consult Captain Simone about it as well.{NOTE:シモーヌ隊長にそのことを相談しようと思ってるんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.98,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Lilia is growing too.{NOTE:リリアも成長したな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.08,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,I heard what you said.{NOTE:話は聞かせてもらった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:12.68,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Captain Simone!{NOTE:シモーヌ隊長。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:14.05,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Mr. Reverto too.{NOTE:リヴェルトさんも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.68,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Debu..!{NOTE:デブ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:17.62,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,..ri.{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:20.72,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,It's Deburi! Why do you always mess it up?{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.12,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,Lilia.{NOTE:リリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:28.05,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,I heard that you want to study the Black Riders.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズなる者たちについて調べたいという意思。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:29.88,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,Of course you have our permission.{NOTE:もちろん許可しよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.35,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.{NOTE:有難うございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:34.38,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,Hey, don't ignore me!{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:37.68,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,We were on our way back to Gildegaran.{NOTE:我々もGildegaranに戻る最中…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:40.15,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,But we overheard a rumor about mysterious Riders…{NOTE:…謎のライダーの話を耳にし…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.35,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,…so we hurried here.{NOTE:…急遽引き返してきたのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.98,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,I heard that Avinia was captured.{NOTE:アユリアがさらわれたって聞いたぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:46.35,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,Is it true?{NOTE:本当なのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.05,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.62,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,I think it's true.{NOTE:本当だと思う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.92,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,Damn.{NOTE:くそ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.68,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,Who would do such thing?{NOTE:なんてやつらんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:57.82,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,They're obviously hunting for the\hKinship Stones all over the place.{NOTE:やつらがあちこちで絆石狩りをしてるのは間違いないようだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:59.82,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,I see.{NOTE:そうなんですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.85,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,I'm worried.{NOTE:心配だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:06.05,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,About that girl, as well as everyone's' Kinship Stones.{NOTE:その少女のことも、皆の絆石も。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.98,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,Investigate all that you can here, Lilia.{NOTE:心ゆくまで調べなさい、リリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:13.72,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,Not just for the squad, but also for your friends.{NOTE:書士隊として、そして、ライダーを共に持つものとして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.95,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,We can't just leave things as they are.{NOTE:この状況を放っておくわけにはいかない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:18.32,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:22.25,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,We will gather all the information we can as well.{NOTE:こっちも出来る限りの情報を集めて知らせるぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:25.72,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,My information network is pretty cool too.{NOTE:ま、見てよな。俺の情報はXXXじゃね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:27.15,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.{NOTE:ありがとうございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.52,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Captain Simone, Mr. Reverto…{NOTE:シモーヌの隊長。リヴェルトさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:35.62,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, don't just skip over me!{NOTE:こらこら、俺をXXXするな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.85,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Thank you, Debu…{NOTE:有難うね、デブ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:44.78,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,Hey, it's…!{NOTE:だからXXXと言え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:45.45,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,…ri.{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.78,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,You're doing this on purpose, aren't you?{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:53.75,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,Is Avinia the girl who survived back then?{NOTE:アユリアはXXXの村のいきも生き残りとか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.25,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,She is.{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:14:00.12,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,I heard that her village holds a lot of secrets.{NOTE:私もあの村には色々な謎があったと聞いています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:02.45,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,I'd better investigate things as well.{NOTE:こちらでも調べてみるつもりです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.95,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,I agree.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.42,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.{NOTE:頼みますぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:13.48,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,Please be patient a little longer.{NOTE:XXX。もう少し辛抱してね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.38,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,We'll be saved for sure.{NOTE:必ず助けるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.78,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hey there!{NOTE:ほらよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:24.35,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,It's meal time.{NOTE:御前の飯だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:32.55,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste if you threw this food away.{NOTE:おともの面倒を見たいなら自分も食わねーと思うたぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.95,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.{NOTE:ありがとうございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.25,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hey, Little girl.{NOTE:お嬢ちゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:49.08,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,I'll say this perfectly clear.{NOTE:一つ言っておく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:51.85,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Right now, you're powerless.{NOTE:今のお前は無力だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.82,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You can't do anything by yourself.{NOTE:一人じゃ何にも出来ない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:58.22,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Naturally, you don't have the key, or the power to break the chains.{NOTE:当然この鎖を鍵を壊す力もない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.05,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Do not forget that.{NOTE:忘れるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:06.85,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Well, it'd be a different story if you had Lars's appetite.{NOTE:ま。ラースの兄貴みたいに鎖を噛み切れたら話は別だがな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:11.95,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,What do you hope to gain from all of this?{NOTE:貴方達の目的は何なんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.65,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,A Kinship Stone, of course.{NOTE:もちろん絆石がありさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:17.15,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,And from the world's best Rider, too.{NOTE:世界一のライダーのな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.22,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.78,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:Ride On!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:22.72,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.15,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.08,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lute will take Navirou.{NOTE:リュートにはナビルーがついている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:36.58,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{\an8}We'll get to see just how useful he really is as a Navigator.{NOTE:本当にナビゲーターとして役に立ってるかどうかは置いといてね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:43.61,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{\an8}That said, we'll also be lending a hand.{NOTE:と言うわけで、俺達も協力さしてもらうことだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:46.21,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,To the other Riders, that is.{NOTE:ライダーさんたちにな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:48.95,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,You look rather weak.{NOTE:なにしても、おまえ弱そうだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:53.71,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{\an8}I may be right now, but I'm aiming to become the world's best Rider.{NOTE:う、今はそうでも夢は世界一のライダーだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.31,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seems impossible if you ask me.{NOTE:それは俺は俺なしじゃ無理だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:58.75,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{\an8}But, you know what?{NOTE:よし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.71,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll become your Navigator.{NOTE:俺がナビゲーターについてやれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:04.51,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,One condition though! You have to call me "senpai".{NOTE:ただし！俺のことは心配だよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:09.01,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,'Aight, senpai.{NOTE:いいぜっす、先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:11.28,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Please take care of me.{NOTE:俺の面倒を見させてやる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.35,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,You're funny, y'know!{NOTE:面白い、お前！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:17.91,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Get off my back.{NOTE:なんだよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.85,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Cheval.{NOTE:—シュヴァルさん。\\N—ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:24.45,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,My coolness should go well with your coolness.{NOTE:クールな僕としてはクールなあなたに興味があります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:26.28,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,Why don't we join our forces?{NOTE:僕とを組みませんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:28.91,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,Sure.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.71,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,We'll be a good team.{NOTE:心強いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:35.51,Default,Chamo,0,0,0,,Floof wants to pair with Mille-Mille.{NOTE:チャモはミルミルと一緒に行きたいでしょにゃー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.05,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Mille-Mille?{NOTE:ミルミル？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.15,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,Then you'll be Floof-Floof.{NOTE:じゃ、あなたはチャモチャモね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:40.51,Default,Chamo,0,0,0,,Hehe.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:43.41,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,Hyoro.{NOTE:ヒョロさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:48.18,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,We're both reserved, so I\hthink we'd work well together.{NOTE:僕達控えめなもの同士、気が合いそうだと思う頃にゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:50.45,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,I think so, too.{NOTE:僕もそんな気がする。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:55.28,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Looks like everyone got their Navigator, Navirou.{NOTE:あはは。皆にナビゲがついたぞ、ナビルー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:17:00.25,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Well, it still doesn't change the fact that Navirou is the best Navigator around.{NOTE:ま、世界一のナビゲーターはナビルーであることに変わりはないだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:03.28,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,I will go with you, Lilia.{NOTE:私はあなたと行くわ、リリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:05.25,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,I want to research them as well.{NOTE:私も色々知りたいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.08,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,The Black Riders.{NOTE:ライダースについて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.81,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Really? That's great! I'm sure we'll be a good team.{NOTE:そうなんだ？よろしくね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:11.38,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,I can be useful too, y'know.{NOTE:な、俺だって役に立つぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:14.45,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,I can fish out information from here and there as well.{NOTE:あちこちに情報も張り巡らすからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.75,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Fake intel could also be useful.{NOTE:それが役に立ってくれそうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.05,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,Right?{NOTE:だろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:21.28,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,…fake intel?{NOTE:XXX？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.05,Default,Deburi,0,0,0,,Of course it's not fake!{NOTE:XXXじゃね！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.11,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,I'm just joking.{NOTE:冗談よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:25.45,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,I expect a lot of you, Debu…{NOTE:期待してるわよ、デブ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:26.31,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Alright!{NOTE:しゃ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.38,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Well then, let's go!{NOTE:それじゃ、行くか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:34.51,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– …ri.\N– Deburi is one word!{NOTE:—XXX！\\N—え？お前だね、普通にデブ言って言え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.08,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,Chief.{NOTE:村長。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.05,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,I'm leaving the village to you.{NOTE:村のこと頼みます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.15,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,We'll be back as soon as possible.{NOTE:早く戻ります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.15,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,Very well.{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.68,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,And Nariki will be staying with us.{NOTE:ナリキもおるしな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.01,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,Exactly.{NOTE:そうじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:48.25,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,Everything will be fine.{NOTE:我々だけども大丈夫じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.15,Default,Stone,0,0,0,,Then, we leave things to you, Mr. Gamigami.{NOTE:頼みますガミガミさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:54.31,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,Don't worry about us.{NOTE:心配にいらん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:18:00.78,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,What is the goal of Black Riders and who are they?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズと言う者たちが何を求め、何をXXしているのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:04.38,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,I want you to research both of these things in great detail.{NOTE:XXX見定めてきて欲しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:07.81,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,However, do not forget to be extremely careful.{NOTE:ただし、くれぐれも気を付けるのじゃと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.18,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Yes sir.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:13.45,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,Um, I don't see Lute anywhere.{NOTE:あの、さっきからリュート先輩が見当たらないんですけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:16.91,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Lute said he wanted to see the village one more time.{NOTE:リュートもう一度村を見てくるって言ってたけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:17.95,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.78,Default,Yoro,0,0,0,,He must be having second thoughts.{NOTE:きっと名残惜しいですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:29.18,Default,Yoro,0,0,0,,After all, you guys just got back.{NOTE:だって、皆帰ってきたばかりですの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.98,Default,Yoro,0,0,0,,And now you're going away again.{NOTE:なのに、又行っちゃうなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:35.21,Default,Yoro,0,0,0,,I'll be lonely.{NOTE:寂しいですの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.08,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,We'll be back soon, Loloa.{NOTE:必ず戻ってくる、XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.31,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,Don't cry.{NOTE:泣かないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:43.25,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,We'll always be connected by our kinship.{NOTE:俺たちはいつだって絆で結ばれてる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:50.61,Default,Yoro,0,0,0,,You're right!{NOTE:そう何ですの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:53.78,Default,Yoro,0,0,0,,Our hearts will always be connected!{NOTE:いつも心は繋がってるんですの！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.01,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:—え。\\N—うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.41,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Alright.{NOTE:ん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.75,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,We're pretty far back in Hakum's woods.{NOTE:しっかり元のハクム村の森に戻ったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:09.75,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.95,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,The Black Blight is gone.{NOTE:黒の凶気は消え去った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.81,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,And now we can go save Avinia without worrying too much.{NOTE:これで安心したアユリアを探しに行けるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:15.65,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:お。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:18.35,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,But I still wonder who they are?{NOTE:でも、なんなんだろうな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.05,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Those Black Riders.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.21,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Hm. It's a mystery.{NOTE:んん。謎だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.98,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hey!{NOTE:よ、よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:30.01,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Rathalos Rider.{NOTE:リオレウスのライダーくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:31.48,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.55,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You've got a sharp look.{NOTE:いいめしてんじゃねーか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:37.48,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,As to be expected from someone who stopped the Black Blight.{NOTE:さすが黒の凶気を止めたライダーだけのことはある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:42.31,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,But I can't bring myself to like you.{NOTE:での、気に入られんだな。お前のこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:44.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Huh? What's with you?{NOTE:は？なんなんだよお前？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.41,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Wait… is that a Rathalos?{NOTE:お？リオレウスか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.31,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,It's huge.{NOTE:でか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.65,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I've never seen a Rathalos like that.{NOTE:あんなにリオレウス見たことない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:59.95,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Surprised? Gale's Rathalos is a rare species.{NOTE:驚いたか？これがゲール様のリオレウス希少種だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.65,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Rare species?{NOTE:希少種？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:02.85,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,I'm Gale.{NOTE:おれはゲール。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:04.61,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,I'm Nuts.{NOTE:俺様はナッツ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:07.61,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,And this is my little friend, Dusk.{NOTE:こいつは俺のダスクだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:09.71,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Charmed to meet you, Lute.{NOTE:よろしくな、リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.91,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,How do you know me?{NOTE:何で俺のこと知ってるんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.58,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Get ready, Lute.{NOTE:用事しろ、リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:16.15,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Look at the way he's hiding his face. He's a suspicious person, for sure!{NOTE:顔隠している怪しすぎだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:19.05,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Wait a second, don't tell me you're…{NOTE:ていうか、ま-まさかお前…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.41,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,A-A Black Rider?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:26.28,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Is it true?{NOTE:そうなのか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.88,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Who knows?{NOTE:どうだろうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:29.35,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,What do you think?{NOTE:どう思う？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.85,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Who knows?{NOTE:どうだろうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.11,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,What do you think?{NOTE:どう思う？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:35.95,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Don't give me that look.{NOTE:でもま、そうみらまえるなって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:39.21,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,We're both riding a\hRathalos, so let's be friends.{NOTE:同じリオレウス乗り通し、仲良くやろうぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:41.75,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Yeah, friends, the very best of friends!{NOTE:そうそう。楽しく楽しく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:45.11,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I heard you've captured Avinia!{NOTE:お前たちがアユリアを連れ去ったって聞いてるの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:46.68,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Give her back!{NOTE:アユリアを返せ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:47.71,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.91,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,You caught me, I won't object to that.{NOTE:ま、それは認めるけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.61,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Then give her back.{NOTE:だったら速く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.88,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Before that…{NOTE:その前に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.45,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Lute.{NOTE:やろーぜ、リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.98,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.78,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Do what?{NOTE:何をやろうと言うのだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.48,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Ain't it obvious?{NOTE:それはもちろん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.51,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Let's have a battle.{NOTE:バトルに決まってるだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.65,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:11.35,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I won't fight another Rider.{NOTE:俺はライダーと戦うつもりはない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:13.81,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I just want you to return Avinia.{NOTE:ユリアを返してもらいたいだけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:15.48,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Is that so?{NOTE:あそう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.41,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,But we have to fight.{NOTE:でも、俺たちは戦うしかないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:19.61,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.18,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Why?{NOTE:何でだよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:22.81,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,What are you…?{NOTE:何でお前ら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.01,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,It's right on your hand.{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.81,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,I want your Kinship Stone.{NOTE:その絆石が欲しいんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:32.38,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,But you probably won't hand it over if I just ask you.{NOTE:でも、くらって言ってもくれねえだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:35.48,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,So there you have it.{NOTE:だったらま、そう言うことな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:36.88,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Lute.{NOTE:リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:39.28,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,I think we should get back to the village.{NOTE:ここは一度XXX方が。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:42.68,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,We won't let you.{NOTE:そうはさせないんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:44.15,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Exactly.{NOTE:そうよこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.71,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Alright, here I go!{NOTE:んじゃ、行くぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:47.68,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Sync Ride!{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:54.35,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What do we do, Lute?{NOTE:どうするリュート？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:03.81,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ride On!{NOTE:Ride On!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:08.71,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:14.68,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Wah.{NOTE:お。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:18.05,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Whew? Lute! Behind us!{NOTE:お？リュート！きた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:18.95,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,He's fast!{NOTE:速い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:20.75,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What speed!{NOTE:何てスピードだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:28.61,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Ratha, go up!{NOTE:上だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:29.95,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!{NOTE:待ってこら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:31.38,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Are you trying to run away?{NOTE:逃すかよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:33.18,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,That's not going to work!{NOTE:逃げ出すか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:40.08,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What a bunch of…{NOTE:な、何てやつらだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:43.05,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Never mind, Navirou's going to help.{NOTE:こう、こうなったら、ナビルーもXXするの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:46.48,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Lilia gave us lots of stuff just in case we ran into trouble.{NOTE:こんな時のために、リリアに色々もらっておいたのにゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:49.75,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,Uhm… Not that, not this either…{NOTE:えと、これもだめ、これもちがう…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:52.48,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,What's this… Ah! Got it!{NOTE:なんだこれ。そ！これ！XXXだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:54.38,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. The-world's-best-rider!{NOTE:世界一のライダーくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:57.11,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,Your Kinship Stone is ours.{NOTE:おまえの絆石はいただきぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:17.55,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,It's nothing personal.{NOTE:大したことなな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.35,0:23:22.75,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Lute here!{NOTE:俺リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:25.08,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,What's with this guy? He's crazy strong!{NOTE:なんだ、あいつはめちゃくちゃ強い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:27.21,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,If I'm going to beat him I need to… well…?{NOTE:対抗するには(XXX・テンションの日)？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:30.71,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,I don't exactly know yet, but I'd better hurry up!{NOTE:よくわからないけどとにかく、急げ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:34.61,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,Next time: "A strong, dangerous and mysterious enemy". Ride On!{NOTE:次回：強くで危ない謎のやつに。Ride On!}
